== Buryat == {{main|Bible translations into Buryat}}
==Chuvash== A new translation into the [[Chuvash language]] was initiated by the [[Russian Bible Society]] in the 1990s, coordinating New Testament translation carried out by the Baptist churches and the Old Testament translation carried out by the Russian Orthodox Church.<ref>UBS World Report, November 1995, 10-11.</ref> The completed Bible translation was published in 2009.<ref name=RBS_Chuvash/>
