==Tuvan== The Institute for Bible Translation has published a [[Tuvan language|Tuvan]] translation of the Bible. They published Mark in 1996, Luke and Acts in 1997, the whole New Testament in 2001, Ruth, Esther, Jonah and Lamentations in 2003, and the Pentateuch, Proverbs and Psalms in 2005. The complete Bible was published in 2011.<ref name=IBT2011/>
